snippet.title: The Dark Queen of Mortholme: Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD AT https://qwertyprophecy.itch.io/mortholme

You are the Dark Queen—the most powerful being of your entire universe. Your lair is breached by an aspiring hero—a pitiful thing, easily crushed.
Except they keep coming back.

A narrative anti-game about an unconventional relationship and the capacity for change.
